eming|Fleming, Joseph B.]], [[Chicago, Rock Island and Pacific Railroad|RI]] 1933–1947 * [[John Murray Forbes|Forbes, John Murray]] (1813–1898), [[Michigan Central Railroad|MC]] 1846–1855, [[Chicago, Burlington and Quincy Railroad|CB&Q]] * [[Samuel W. Fordyce|Fordyce, Samuel W.]] (1840–1919), [[St. Louis, Arkansas and Texas Railway|SLA&T]] 1886–1889, [[St. Louis Southwestern Railway|SSW]] 1890–1898, [[Kansas City Southern Railway|KCS]] 1900 * [[Walter S. Franklin (PRR)|Franklin, Walter S.]], [[Pennsylvania Railroad|PRR]] 1948–1954, [[Long Island Rail Road|LIRR]] 1954–1955 * [[Donald V. Fraser|Fraser, Donald V.]], [[Missouri-Kansas-Texas Railroad|MKT]] 1945–1956 * [[William A. Frederick|Frederick, William A.]], [[California Northern Railroad|CFNR]] 1993– * [[Alan Furth|Furth, Alan]], [[Southern Pacific Railroad|SP]] 1979–1982
